Package sailpoint.api

Interface Summary
EmailNotifier The interface of an object that can send notifications.
PersistenceManager Interface implemented by classes that provide persistence services.
SailPointContext The primary API for accessing the persistent store and performing core system operations.
 

Class Summary
Differencer Utility class to compare various objects and generate a summary of the differences.
Differencer.AccountItemComparator  
Differencer.BaseComparator<T> Common comparator implementation shared by the class-specific comparators.
Differencer.BundleListFilter A ListFilter that only includes bundles that reference the application passed into the constructor.

Differencer.EntitlementGroupComparator Deep equality comparison for EntitlementGroups.
Differencer.EntitlementSnapshotComparator Deep equality comparison for EntitlementSnapshots.
Differencer.IdentitySnapshotComparator Deep equality comparison for IdentitySnapshots.
Differencer.LinkSnapshotComparator Deep equality comparison for LinkSnapshots.
Differencer.LinkSnapshotListFilter A ListFilter that only includes LinkSnapshots for the application passed into the constructor.
Differencer.PermissionComparator Deep equality comparison for Permissions.
Differencer.RoleAssignmentSnapshotComparator  
Differencer.RoleTargetComparator  
Differencer.ScorecardComparator Deep equality comparison for Scorecards.
Emailer A service that can send emails and capture error messages.
EncodingUtil Utility class for hash or encrypt Identity secret, based on setting in system configuration.
EntitlementCorrelator The EntitlementCorrelator inspects identities and calculates assigned and detected roles and entitlement exceptions based on the attributes on the links.
IdentityService A service layer that deals with identities.
Matchmaker The evaluation engine for the IdentitySelector object.
Matchmaker.CubeMatcher Extension of JavaMatcher used with Filter evaluation.
ObjectUtil Utility class providing methods to load and analyze SailPointObject subclasses.
PersistenceManager.LockParameters Encapsulation of lock parameters.
PolicyUtil Utilities for analyzing policies and policy violations.
PolicyUtil.ApplicationSummary Model for entitlements on a specific application account.
PolicyUtil.EntitlementSummary Model for representing entitlements related to SOD violations.
PolicyUtil.ItemSummary Model for one entitlement in an application.
PolicyUtil.RoleSummary Represents a collection of application-specific entitlements, either "free" (the name is null) or associated with a role.
Provisioner Utility class to process ProvisioningProjects and ProvisioningPlans.
RequestManager A class providing an API for managing the request processor and submitting asynchronous requests.
SailPointFactory Factory service for SailPointContexts.
ScopeService Service to deal with scopes.
ScopeService.DeletionOptions DeletionOptions provide information about what to do with scope references when a scope is deleted.
TaskManager A utility class providing task management services.
Terminator Utility class that can delete SailPointObject subclasses while carefully pruning references to them from other objects.
